data.description: THIS IS THE ONE!!! This charming, well-maintained BRICK home is just awaiting your creativity! This home also offers a full basement, garage and additional attic space for storage. This beautiful home is conveniently located within one mile of Gypsy Hill Park. This home is also within three miles of downtown Staunton, offering a wide variety of great restaurants, shops and activities! The oversized lot features a large backyard that makes the PERFECT setting for grilling, entertaining and watching the fireworks.  This one won't last long! Schedule your showing today!
